     :desc:	Continuously send control commands to DO index specified in :ref:`xmlattr-plcPNTDstIndex` of the communication protocol instance :ref:`xmlattr-plcPNTDstDevice`
		for as long as PLC point position is :include-arg:`1`.
		Outgoing control commands will have a qualifier ON.
		A commands will be sent to the destination protocol instance continuously with an interval of 1sec.
		Sending of commands stops when PLC point position is no longer :include-arg:`1` or any of the quality bits [:lemonobgtext:`IV NT BL NT`] are set.
		Please note, the command queue is purged instantly when outstation goes offline.
		This means no previous commands will be sent when outstation goes online again.
